courageous, (708,13)a cultivated as well as of a capacious mind(220,8)tastes are like my own, to approve or amend my plans. How would such a
friend repair the faults of your poor(1250,8)! I am too ardent in execution
and too impatient of difficulties. But it is a still greater evil to me
