safety of others is committed to my care.

I cannot describe to you my sensations on the near prospect of my
undertaking. It is impossible to communicat(93,9)a conception of
the trembling(120,10), half pleasurable and half fearful, with which
I am preparing to depart. I am going to unexplored regions, to “the
land of mi(931,8)now,” but(455,9)kill no albatross; therefore do not
be alarmed(865,8)(406,8)r if I sh(992,8)e back(284,9)s worn and
